  guniqhudid 10
  rotatesprite x y 40960 0 20947 shade wep_pal 4096 windowx1 windowy1 windowx2 windowy2
  break
case 8
case 9
case 12
case 13
  state gunpushback_display
  guniqhudid 10
  rotatesprite x y 40960 0 20947 shade wep_pal 4096 windowx1 windowy1 windowx2 windowy2
  break
case 10
case 11
